{"tid":1874783,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"我要poly 研發個快速測試機變返做made in hk!","createTime":"2020-02-11T11:31:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T08:27:49.000Z","uid":250506,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"dacb919c8fbffb0723c8703198e0679150d449d0","tid":1874783,"uid":250506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T11:31:59.000Z","msg":"以下文字轉自facebook<br />\n📣LIKE 完請廣傳 好人一生平安<br />\n<br />\n有關資助 #Poly  研發既最新消息：<br />\n#唔洗靠政府 <br />\n#唔洗靠眾籌<br />\n<br />\n今日睇完報導立即電郵Poly 查詢捐款方法，剛收到Home Office Staff 親自致電詳細解釋Poly 既情況<br />\n<br />\n資料如下：<br />\n<br />\n1. 捐款方法-填Form<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.polyu.edu.hk/aado/do/donation_forms/2014/ConFormA.doc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.polyu.edu.hk%2Faado%2Fdo%2Fdonation_forms%2F2014%2FConFormA.doc&d=e9hI6ag5UTzhCSVhase9yAomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=ec6c4788\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.polyu.edu.hk/aado/do/donation_forms/2014/ConFormA.doc</a><br />\n<br />\n✅於捐款表格上寫明要捐款既項目<br />\n     「款項用作與武漢肺炎、治療病毒、防疫有關既項目」<br />\n<br />\n✅或者大家會都集中幫助「病毒快測科研」，Admin 姐姐提醒，理大同時研發緊布口罩及消毒潔手液，會捐贈弱勢，所以希望大家都能夠關注<br />\n<br />\n⚠️相對眾籌1 click搞掂，而家又要填form交form過數真係好「麻煩」，但希望動過「捐款」善念既每一個都能夠做找數真漢子。<br />\n如果怕煩而放棄捐款，等國家救你啦，唔好旨意用Made In HK既野啦🤬<br />\n<br />\n2. 捐款前，請大家看看相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/151909049548/posts/10158003090659549/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F151909049548%2Fposts%2F10158003090659549%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=e9hI6ag5UTzhCSVhase9yAomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=106bb003\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/151909049548/posts/10158003090659549/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1507869-20200211.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1507869-20200211.htm&d=e9hI6ag5UTzhCSVhase9yAomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=fd85fb45\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1507869-20200211.htm&h=44c6e11f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1507869-20200211.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1505816-20200131.htm?archive_date=2020-01-31\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1505816-20200131.htm%3Farchive_date%3D2020-01-31&d=e9hI6ag5UTzhCSVhase9yAomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=4e7c8f1a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1505816-20200131.htm%3Farchive_date%3D2020-01-31&h=f6ac19b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1505816-20200131.htm?archive_date=2020-01-31</a>"},{"pid":"d13f7b3f019bc59b906709f39824806a015b6aa6","tid":1874783,"uid":250506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T11:32:22.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"01e07b7e4c99622c88b907dc9b6e9bcd749732eb","tid":1874783,"uid":250506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T11:32:37.000Z","msg":"Push!"},{"pid":"83f7ef16044594eeacccae58621ce43017053f16","tid":1874783,"uid":250506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T11:32:47.000Z","msg":"推呀！"},{"pid":"7967553e0ce2829951022f126cda600899836ec6","tid":1874783,"uid":250506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T11:33:02.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"8fd5854b4d6dd335c54e25c29b59a7f12081d4b1","tid":1874783,"uid":250506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T11:33:13.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"248116e3158ea3e8b5922cb37ebb62c137f5a5f2","tid":1874783,"uid":190141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T11:33:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b2f998b35d78c45861cb264ecae0e68d76345d8","tid":1874783,"uid":263367,"like":0,"dislike